      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz trim Deenahm/ pa-\nangstinahs Waraüis tawu Gal-\nwu / un eezels tew atkaſtawâ\nAmmataâ / unn tu dohti Waraüm\nto Bifkeri winna Rohkâ / pehz\nto pirmajn Eeraddunu / kad tu\nwinna Dsehreena-Dewejs biji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr peeminni man-\nnis / kad tew labbi klahfees / un\ndarri/luhdsams/Schehlastibu pee\nman / unn peeminni mannis pee\nWaraüis / unn darri/ ka es islaists\ntohpu no fcha Namina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es efimu fagschu no-\nsagts / no tahs Eebreezu-Sem-\nmes/ nedg arri es ko fauna efimu\ndarrijs/ ka tee mann fchinni Bed-\nré irr eemettuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tas Maisu-Zeppe-\njo Wirsneeks redſeja/ ka tas labbi\nbij tsstabstijis / ẜazzija tas uhs\nJahsepu / iman arri bij Sapnis/\nun rangi / trihs balti Kurwji bija\nus mannu Galwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wirfejâ Kurwi bija no\nwiſſada Waraüis Ehdeena / kas\nBekkera-Zeppums/ unn tee Putni\nehde no ta Kurwja / us mannu\nGalwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Jahseps unn\nẜazzija: Schi irr winna Jsstab-\nstifchana / tee trihs Kurwji irr\nrihs Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz trim Deenahm\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notiff\nDeenâ / Waraüis Dsim\nnâ / ka wiꞥſch wiſſeem\nKalpeem Dſihres padarr\nwiꞥſch pa-angstinaja ta\nna“ Dewejo Wirsneeka\nun ta Maises-Zeppejo W\nGalwu starp faweem\nkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un eezechle atkaſt\nreena“ Dewejo Wirsneet\nWeeta / unn tas dewe to\nWaraüim Rohkâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Maises\nWirsneeku likke wiꞥſch\nitt ka teem Jahseps bi\nstijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr to D\nDewejo Wirsneeks ne pe\nJahsepa/ bet peemirfe w\n"
